ðŸ’° Personal Expense Tracker

A simple web app to track expenses (Add, Edit, Delete, View Summary, Search features).

---

Tech Stack:
- Node.js
- Express
- SQLite
- EJS
- Bootstrap 5

---

How to Run:

1. Clone the repository to your local system.
2. Open terminal in the project folder.
3. Install dependencies:

   npm install
   (If package.json doesn't exist, first run: npm init -y)
   npm install express body-parser sqlite3 ejs

4. Start the server:
   node server.js
5. Open your browser and go to:

   http://localhost:3000
6. Use the web system: Add, Edit, Delete, Filter/Search, View Summary.

demo video: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SGH0jNeAP9rZYXAEwcAawrt--JIokHBi/view?usp=sharing

